        <abstract>
            <p>Is forwarding the writing machine to Carl Semper.</p>
            <p>Is glad FD has taken up his old friends, the twiners.</p>
            <p>Hopes to get heliotropic aerial roots from J. D. Hooker. Asks FD to find out whether any moulds or roots are apheliotropic. Is puzzled by heliotropism in subterranean roots.</p>
        </abstract>
